姫様に見とれちゃんだって
They say they're captivated by the princess

738
00:54:10,280 --> 00:54:12,780
やれやれなのらね
Good grief, isn't it?

739
00:54:12,780 --> 00:54:15,980
夢を夢見て
Dreaming a dream

740
00:54:15,980 --> 00:54:19,080
恋に恋して生きていたい
I want to live while being in love with love

741
00:54:19,080 --> 00:54:21,080
だから
So

742
