サンゴ礁 白い砂浜も綺麗
Coral reefs, the white sandy beaches are also beautiful

768
00:55:44,288 --> 00:55:45,688
そこに んなっしょい！！
Over there, Nanshoi!!

769
00:55:45,888 --> 00:55:47,188
んなっしょい！！ んなっしょい！！
Nanshoi!! Nanshoi!!

770
00:55:47,388 --> 00:55:48,888
輝く私
The shining me

771
